summary: Simpler is an AI productivity app that helps users prioritize and organize tasks to focus on what truly matters. It offers a free trial and a lifetime ownership option with a money-back guarantee.

useCaseText: Easy article rewriting for SEO improvement.
summary: This website offers a free article rewriter tool that uses advanced AI engines to rewrite complete articles quickly, resulting in original and well-written content. It also offers premium features such as shortening, expanding, using formal tone, and simplifying tone for more sophisticated paraphrasing.

useCaseText: Identified sales triggers, personalized text snippets.
summary: Creatext is a website that offers personalized text snippets generated by AI for trigger-led growth. It helps businesses find information about their prospects on the internet and build customized AI solutions to reach the right customers with the right message at the right time. The site also allows users to buy highly-specific leads or create custom lead lists to bring focus into their CRM and stop wasting time on irrelevant prospects.
